graph LR
    TrustyAI[TrustyAI Service Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    TrustyAI -->|orchestration| Kubernetes[Kubernetes 1.19+]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    TrustyAI -.->|routes & OAuth| OpenShift[OpenShift 4.6+]
    TrustyAI -.->|ServiceMonitor| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator v0.64.1]
    TrustyAI -->|TLS certs| CertMgr[cert-manager /<br/>service-ca]

    %% Internal RHOAI Dependencies
    TrustyAI -->|payload logging| KServe[KServe]
    TrustyAI -->|payload logging| ModelMesh[ModelMesh Serving]
    TrustyAI -->|metrics export| Prometheus[Prometheus]

    %% Integration Points (ODH Components)
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|UI management| TrustyAI
    DSPipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|automated monitoring| TrustyAI

    %% External Services
    TrustyAI -->|API access| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]
    TrustyAI -->|authentication| OAuthService[OpenShift OAuth Service]
    TrustyAI -->|data persistence| PVC[PersistentVolume Storage]

    %% Managed Resources
    TrustyAI -.->|creates| Deployments[Deployments]
    TrustyAI -.->|creates| Services[Services]
    TrustyAI -.->|creates| Routes[OpenShift Routes]
    TrustyAI -.->|creates| ServiceMonitors[ServiceMonitors]
    TrustyAI -.->|creates| PVCs[PersistentVolumeClaims]

    %% CRDs
    TrustyAICR[TrustyAIService CR<br/>trustyai.opendatahub.io/v1alpha1] -->|watched by| TrustyAI
    TrustyAI -->|patches| InferenceServiceCR[InferenceService CR<br/>serving.kserve.io]
    TrustyAI -->|patches| ServingRuntimeCR[ServingRuntime CR<br/>serving.kserve.io]

